{"tid":399960,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"佐佐木希於新劇《雨が降ると君は優しい》飾演性上癮人妻","createTime":"2017-09-14T11:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T09:10:57.000Z","uid":11354,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"37e7255a28ea080fef47cb5970b4031b1c175a69","tid":399960,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T11:31:36.000Z","msg":"日本超人氣女模特兒兼演員佐佐木希，將於新劇《雨が降ると君は優しい》中飾演性上癮人妻。《雨が降ると君は優しい》由曾經編寫《高校教師》、《美しい人》的野島伸司負責編劇，佐佐木希飾演性上癮人妻立木彩，她雖然已經曾與其他男性發生關係，並對於無法自我控制慾望而感到非常苦惱，但依然深愛丈夫。丈夫立木信夫（玉山鉄二 飾）得知後依然深愛著她，而編劇就是想從中呈現兩夫婦身心之間的衝突。預告中亦都出現了佐佐木希多場床上戲，實在是佐佐木希演藝生涯中的一大突破！新劇《雨が降ると君は優しい》將於 9 月 16 日起每周六在 Hulu 播出，想收看的朋友敬請留意。"},{"pid":"25009d24e1f2ef5dc7194f7e4b7d2b9dd3fc058a","tid":399960,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T11:34:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6b91uIrx31M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6b91uIrx31M&d=XK27kAoQLMx7dxFTeMI7ur%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=da8105f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6b91uIrx31M</a>"},{"pid":"632437f86d31e1affbb20cd3898be62fd143f007","tid":399960,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"有冇精華片段睇下先"},{"pid":"c213d130ac700196f85c279d15a3b9fdcf9a56b6","tid":399960,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T11:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5a411956cfc3a40027335f2d0068152d83cea9","tid":399960,"uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T19:08:30.000Z","msg":"睇錯佐々木あき"},{"pid":"e1e970bf29b6b4a631e6ee902781899feaa9954a","tid":399960,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T20:53:39.000Z","msg":"無波"},{"pid":"c03518b6c67ffa36ca40b8dd021a64969f577e37","tid":399960,"uid":31405,